title: Install Qutebrowser on Ubuntu Using Nix
tags: _method @zettel nix ubuntu qutebrowser
roam-id: c009d083-693a-4881-a323-b2ca04c32724
type: text/markdown

``` shell
nix-channel --add https://github.com/nix-community/nixGL/archive/main.tar.gz nixgl && nix-channel --update
nix-env -iA nixgl.auto.nixGLDefault
nix-env -iA nixpkgs.qutebrowser
nixGL qutebrowser
```
